==Description== <!--T:2-->

<!--T:3-->
The [[FreeGrid_BitCartridgeHolder|FreeGrid Bit Cartridge Holder]] tool allows the user to create a FreeGrid object.

<!--T:16-->
This tool is part of the [[FreeGrid_Workbench|FreeGrid Workbench]], an [[External_workbenches|external workbench]] that can be installed with the [[Image:Std_AddonMgr.svg|24px]] [[Std_AddonMgr|Addon Manager]].

==Usage== <!--T:5-->

<!--T:6-->
# Select  {{Button|[[Image:FreeGrid_BitCartridgeHolder.svg|16px]] [[FreeGrid_BitCartridgeHolder|Bit Cartridge Holder]]}} from the FreeGrid tools.
# A bit catridge holder will be created with the default values established on the preferences page.
# Click on the storage box object and go the [[Tree_View|Tree View]] and change the parameters you need.

